al leadership in history.<br />\n<br />\n制度問題，普選解決！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"制度問題，普選解決！"},{"pid":"0f4e0a5731773f7f919b43bed46fe50114b02b8b","tid":1502944,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:30:00.000Z","msg":"制度問題，普選解決"},{"pid":"c1e73ac283dcaa0d140d119b4960de35d085bfef","tid":1502944,"uid":313869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:30:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n很遺憾，李先生為我校舊生，我們為此致歉。 李先生行為不旦有辱校譽，亦不符道德水平。我們促請其公開道歉，承擔責任！<br />\n<br />\n[割蓆聲明] 馬崇真與恒大學生會長割蓆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a91463c0f26cf6a318cde9fdeddec02655acef68","tid":1502944,"uid":178320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:38:57.000Z","msg":"今日實測，西柏林海報+Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act有好多鬼影相！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d8611d58378c7518a14021bf2177e246b9fd85","tid":1502944,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2c6dcdd1c542404b0fc7085fd85619d32d70d5","tid":1502944,"uid":7427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T21:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79602ee06ee9e2f281791149492aff83b812430","tid":1502944,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T21:26:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"399a1fedf7ce3a79b51e8c863f8125ad6e10bf98","tid":1502944,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl