,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"記住，想擴大文宣威力、脫離同溫層，<br />\n要擴大文宣既可能性，<br />\n中立淺藍只會自私地關心自己既衣食住行<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向：<br />\n- 放大緊急法既生活影響<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snwVMdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnwVMdn.jpg&h=58d66585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大林鄭既攬炒慾望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT8dxUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT8dxUs.jpg&h=d3e77a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asdJaF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasdJaF8.jpg&h=996481da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHbe1NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHbe1NO.jpg&h=a377df13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 一人一個淺黃、中立既經濟行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YtJaKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YtJaKn.jpg&h=c45f7608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nRnrhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nRnrhK.jpg&h=b96ff78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DK00cXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDK00cXM.jpg&h=2a6e1403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大tg既害處，影響飲食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKrq8t1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKrq8t1.jpg&h=91688cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2pwjAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx